<chapter xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"  xml:id="ch_counting">
  <title>Listing and Counting</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
      Since listing and counting are at the heart of discrete mathematics,
      we begin our journey there in <xref ref="sec_listing"></xref> Organized Listing,
      <xref ref="sec_counting_steps_cases"></xref>
      Counting with Steps and Cases,
      <xref ref="sec_counting_subsets"></xref> Counting Subsets,
      and <xref ref="sec_bit_strings"></xref> Counting Bit Strings.
    </p>
  </introduction>
